data.name: cow for cow
pball's dark 4chan theme
data.description:
This is a highly modified copy of Awesum Dark *chan Style. I started using that theme years ago and modified it to my liking and when features and stuff changed on 4chan. I use it with 4chan X so it might not look complete other wise.

I will continue to update as 4chan changes, just give me a bit of time to remember to update here.

data.name: 巴哈姆特動畫瘋暗化版 (DARKMODE for ani.gamer.com.tw 基於阿尼妹中毒)
data.description:
鑑於原版作者hollen9不再更新 本修正版乃以其為基礎之修正

主要修正內容:
1.播放區色彩修正
2.右上選單、觀看紀錄、評分、年齡驗證、付費方案、延長效期等頁面新增DARKMODE
3.各按鈕顏色修正
4.播放器選單顏色修正
(以上修正基於2020-05-23 之巴哈姆特動畫瘋網頁 ani.gamer.com.tw )
